{"tid":1692802,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"大家去開尖沙咀可唔可以順手 懲罰埋呢間黃店?","createTime":"2019-11-04T08:53:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-06T12:55:55.000Z","uid":73934,"like":39,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c88b6bf6760d140ad00dee1a09f542457efccd50","tid":1692802,"uid":73934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T08:53:56.000Z","msg":"琴晚夜晚食飯時間入到去1個人都冇，老闆係度睇緊4台直播，本身都冇咩點理，只係覺得有d慘，食物質素唔講，費事比人話打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，同埋我對食冇咩要求加只係食甜品，但老闆堅nice,有同我地傾吓計吹吓水，同埋講佢地海南雞飯係招牌菜，因為我都係做生意又係好淡 所以大家都都講左句一齊加油,跟著見到張單。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/25Vtorf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F25Vtorf.jpg&h=70d0a9f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我只想講仲有好多店係度默默耕耘緊，就算冇生意都係度支持香港人，好難得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n間野就係唇茶對便，上3樓，希望大家去開尖沙咀 懲罰龍門冰室同唇茶嗰陣時可以順手懲罰埋佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd7c24eb08b10cbf754855180b62b5bf58ba2c43","tid":1692802,"uid":12879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T08:55:41.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3582cead07544a3a32951ac72c98c2a95e5e2140","tid":1692802,"uid":109820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T09:02:34.000Z","msg":"推順便借位<br />\n<br />\n【認真參考日本社運】想行得遠過藍絲，不如唔好再鬧同路人啲ig？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1692734\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1692734</a>"},{"pid":"144b05d9c0bd658637dc9f0b47dca144b6745688","tid":1692802,"uid":73934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T11:02:02.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e97767feb5f75ada3405880adee77ae5c9d3a8a7","tid":1692802,"uid":73934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T13:33:06.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e1482b9e0e27a5099cff1a570a9cb9d1adb5b40e","tid":1692802,"uid":293539,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T13:37:29.000Z","msg":"名又